Turkey's trade deficit widen 382 mln dlrs April 275 mln March 273 mln April 1986 State Statistics Institute said. The deficit quarter 1987 widen 1.23 billion dlrs 1.20 billion earlier. April export total 702 mln dlrs compare import 1.08 billion. Exports month worth 2.69 billion dlrs compare import 3.92 billion. REUTER 